<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='417000' id='t-417000'>Or is it a bug, a mistake in the system --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='420000' id='t-420000'>this religious stuff is just something</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='422000' id='t-422000'>that happens when the wires cross in the brain --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='425000' id='t-425000'>Jill has a stroke and she has this religious experience,</span>
